.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3256396/chinese-north-korean-officials-vow-boost-strategic-ties-beijing-talks?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国澳大利亚煤炭进口激增，取代俄罗斯成为最大供应国，但高科技产品“缓慢燃烧”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3256393/chinas-australian-coal-imports-surge-replacing-russia-top-supplier-hi-tech-products-be-slow-burner?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着北京和堪培拉关系的改善，2024年前两个月中国从澳大利亚进口的煤炭同比增长3,188%，达到13.4亿美元。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3256393/chinas-australian-coal-imports-surge-replacing-russia-top-supplier-hi-tech-products-be-slow-burner?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>北京扣押被中国海警抓获后“谎报身份”的“台湾士兵”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3256399/beijing-holding-taiwanese-soldier-who-lied-about-identity-after-being-picked-mainland-chinese?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>台湾事务办公室表示，周一，这名男子和一名同伴在福建省沿海的船只失去动力后被救起。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:30:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3256399/beijing-holding-taiwanese-soldier-who-lied-about-identity-after-being-picked-mainland-chinese?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国研究表明竹子可以提供“类似于牛奶”的新蛋白质来源</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3256171/bamboo-can-provide-new-source-protein-similar-cows-milk-chinese-study?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国科学家表示，竹子具有一系列健康益处，可以帮助养活不断增长的全球人口。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3256171/bamboo-can-provide-new-source-protein-similar-cows-milk-chinese-study?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美团第四季度营收因订单强劲而增长，新举措亏损进一步收窄</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3256388/meituans-fourth-quarter-revenue-jumps-strong-orders-while-losses-new-initiatives-nar